Package budget

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Annotation
    This class represents an annotation that is present in a budget to be used as reference by the salesperson.
    Attachment
    This class represents a file that is added at the end of the budget when it is printed.
    Budget
    This class represents a Budget or an Offer.
    Client
    This class represents a Client as the person or company whom the budget is created.
    Cover
    This class represents a cover available to be selected as the cover of the budget when it is printed.
    Document
    This class represents a document that is present in a budget to be used as reference by the salesperson.
    Price
    This class consists in the representation of each price and the date since it is valid.
    Product
    This class represents a product.
    Salesperson
    This class represents a Salesperson as the person that can access to the system and create budgets to the clients.
    Section
    This class represents a section of products in a budget.
    SectionProduct
    This class represents a product and its information in a line of a budget.
    User
    This class represents a User as a person that can access to the system.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Permission
    This class represents the different types of permissions that a user can have assigned.
    UserType
    This class represents the different types of users that can access to the system.
